Module Stratego
Package com.stratego

Class Player

java.lang.Object
com.stratego.Player
public class Player
extends java.lang.Object
Contains a player's identifying information and information relevant to the number of remaining pieces of each type that a player can still place down.
Author:
Jeremiah Allsbrook, Clint Mooney, James Ford
